" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 560px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Peace sign to assess ulnar nerve motor function",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 540px; height: 405px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Injury to the ulnar nerve impairs function of the dorsal and palmar interossei making patients unable to abduct and adduct their fingers. This can be tested by having the patient make a peace sign, as shown in the photograph.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
